name.k: Tomb of the Mask: Pixel Maze
Tomb of the Mask: Fun Games

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Speed is survival in this devilishly fast tomb-raiding arcade game. Like some glorious mix of Indiana Jones and Pac-Man, you race from room to room, nabbing all the coins you can while staying ahead of an ever-moving (and lethal) wall. With its crafty mazes, tricky traps, simple controls, and eye-popping retro minimalism, its an experience youll happily lose yourself in.
